'''House Hirskaala''' was a trading concern operating from [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. It was founded in the wake of the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] being pushed out of the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]] in the [[Trade Wars]]. They had offices in [[Gadrin]] near the center of the town.

In [[31 BBY/Legends|31 BBY]], an employee of House Hirskaala named [[Darin]] was kidnapped by [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] dressed in stolen Hirskaala security uniforms.<ref name="ACP">{{LivingForce|Eye of the Sun: A Cularin Presence}}</ref> Within a month of that incident, several Hirskaala security employees disappeared themselves to join the [[Cularin resistance]], including Hirskaala's head of security, [[Nim'Ri]]. [[Yaeger Doru]] became head of security during Nim'Ri's absence.<ref name="TRW">{{LivingForce|Eye of the Sun: The Resistance Within}}</ref>

